dwm-mail-mon - mail monitor for dwm

OVERVIEW
    This is a simple program to monitor a list of directories using inotify(7) 
    and update dwm's status bar when a file is added or removed. It's intended 
    to be used with a list of Maildirs to display the number of new messages.

CONFIGURATION
   Modify the watches[] array in dwm-mail-mon.c to include the list of paths you 
   wish to monitor, as well as the name to display.

